fr.data.purchase

Class Purchase

  • java.lang.Object
    • fr.data.purchase.Purchase

  • public class Purchase
extends java.lang.Object
    Purchase class. This class is use when a purchase is made by a customer. It has the amount of the purchase, an id, a date, a tag that say if there was a prescription, the number of product bought and the list of them and the customer store id.
    Version:
    2.0 26 Apr 2021
    Author:
    Max Labbe, Mathieu Way, Ophelie Foucault
